## Summary:
PASS (infrastructure): 5/8 steps — auth, notebook CRUD, source upload, export, list endpoints
BLOCKED (external deps): 3/8 steps — audio, slides, chat (require AI provider API key)

The 3 blocked steps are NOT code bugs — they are correctly returning errors when
no AI model is configured. To unblock, set OPENAI_API_KEY or run Ollama locally.

## Bugs Found and Fixed:
1. SET LOCAL app.tenant_id: PostgreSQL doesn't support parameterized SET
2. audit_logs missing updated_at: BaseRepository assumed all tables have it
3. BaseRepository deleted_at: assumed all tables have soft-delete column
4. UUID→string: PostgreSQL returns UUID objects, Pydantic expects strings
5. Loguru format error: error messages containing { } crashed the formatter
6. docker-compose backup sidecar: && syntax fails in BusyBox ash
